Popular Nigerian singer, Jaywon has gifted himself a Mercedes Benz ML350 as he nears turning a year older.  Jaywon and his new car Nigerian singer, Jaywon who will be a year older on June 6th has gotten himself an early birthday gift. The singer took to Instagram to show off his new whip. He shared photos and a video to the amazement of his fans. In his caption, he explained that he wants to ‘spoil himself a little’. He wrote: “Birthday gift came early.”Make I spoil Myself small!!! Shout out to @m_jautos trusted and reliable for clean automobile!!! Baba na G wagon next oooo.” Source:http://Tori.ng